bel style="color:#FFDB00;" class="_span">≥10W</label></view><view style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-left:75rpx;"><view class="yellow"></view><text class="introduceYellowText">普通用户业绩量计算标准：</text></view><view class="yellowContent">个人订单金额×100%＋通过用户专属注册链接注册的用户订单金额×100%</view><view style="display:flex;align-items:center;margin-left:75rpx;margin-top:30rpx;"><view class="yellow"></view><text class="introduceYellowText">合伙人业绩量计算标准：</text></view><view class="yellowContent">个人订单金额×100%＋通过合伙人专属注册链接注册的用户订单金额×100%＋通过名下用户及合伙人的专属注册链接注册的用户订单金额×100%＋名下其他用户订单金额×10%</view><view class="yellowFooter"><view>例:</view><view>A合伙人邀请B用户注册</view><view>B用户邀请C用户注册</view><view>C用户邀请D用户注册</view><view>D用户邀请F用户注册</view><view>则A合伙人的业绩量＝A的订单金额×100%＋B的订单金额×100%＋C的订单金额×100%＋D的订单金额×10%＋F的订单金额×10%......以此类推</view></view></view><view class="introduceContent3"><view class="introduceTitle2" style="top:-40rpx;">奖池活动规则</view><view class="currencyTitle" style="margin-left:44rpx;margin-top:-40rpx;">普通用户权益：</view><view style="margin-left:47rpx;display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:20rpx;"><view class="blue">1.</view><text class="blueText">雷猫商城全部成交金额的1%会注入奖池</text></view><view style="margin-left:47rpx;display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:20rpx;"><view class="blue">2.</view><text class="blueText">雷猫商城合伙人有权参与奖池瓜分</text></view><view style="margin-left:47rpx;display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:20rpx;"><view class="blue">3.</view><text class="blueText">达成分阶段目标，即可享受阶段目标对应比例的奖池分红</text></view><view style="margin-left:47rpx;display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:20rpx;"><view class="blue">4.</view><text class="blueText">完成更高阶段目标的合伙人，同样参与低阶段目标奖池分红</text></view><view style="margin-left:47rpx;display:flex;align-items:center;"><view class="blue">5.</view><text class="blueText">若分阶段目标无人达成，则该阶段对应奖池金额累计至下期活动</text></view><view class="jztBg1" style="{{'background-image:'+('url('+jztBg1+')')+';'}}"></view><view class="jztText1"><view>总奖池=商城总营业额*1%</view><view>分阶段标准达成，即可享受奖池阶段分红</view></view><view class="jztBg2" style="{{'background-image:'+('url('+jztBg2+')')+';'}}"><view style="position:absolute;color:#0A9EFE;font-weight:bold;">例:</view></view><view class="jztText2"><view>若A用户，活动期间业绩量为50W,商城总营业额为1000w,则奖池总金额为1000w*1%=10w</view><view>该用户可获得的奖池分红为：</view><view style="max-width:658rpx;">（10w*20%÷1）+（10w*20%÷5）+（10w*20%÷10）+<view class="_br"></view>（10w*20%÷15）+（10w*20%÷20）≈2.8w</view></view></view><view class="introduceContent4"><view class="introduceTitle2" style="top:-28rpx;">雷猫积分使用规则</view><view style="margin-top:-20rpx;"><view class="footerText"><label style="color:#FEDA01;" class="_span">1.</label>预缴本商城出售设备的电费</view><view class="footerText"><label style="color:#FEDA01;" class="_span">2.</label>购买本商城的设备</view><view class="footerText"><label style="color:#FEDA01;" class="_span">3.</label>转让给其他商城用户</view></view><view class="kefuText">雷猫商城专属客服扫码添加</view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['handleDownloadQrIMg',['https://www.leimaominer.com/public/images/webservice/service.png']]]]]}}" class="kefuImg" bindtap="__e"></view></view></view>